## React + TypeScript

	•	Mature UI ecosystem, graph libraries, intentionally minimal three-archetype interface well within range.

## Vite

	•	Fast HMR, minimal config, builds static assets served by Express.

##Express

	•	Thin Node server. Serves React bundle and exposes API routes for DB and FSRS. Single process, trivially containerized.

## better-sqlite3

	•	Synchronous SQLite binding for Node. Fastest JS SQLite option, WAL mode, full constraint enforcement. Single file on a Docker volume.

## Drizzle ORM

	•	Schema-as-code, type-safe queries, direct SQL output, migration runner. Maps 1:1 to the schema already designed.

## ts-fsrs

	•	Maintained TypeScript FSRS-5 port. 19 weights, scheduler and optimizer both included. Runs in the same Node process as Express — no sidecar, no IPC, no boundary.

## Docker

	•	Express + React static assets + SQLite volume mount. Single container, single port. docker run -p 3000:3000 -v ./data:/data.

